### Update an existing auto part (Assuming ID 1 exists from previous tests)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/parts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
"name": "Brake Pads - Premium Ceramic",
"sku": "BRK-CER-001",
"stockQuantity": 150,
"minimumRequired": 20,
"manufacturer": "Brembo"
}

### Attempt to update a non-existent part (Testing our defensive 404 response)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/parts/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ghost Part",
  "sku": "GST-000",
  "stockQuantity": 10,
  "minimumRequired": 5,
  "manufacturer": "Unknown"
}

### Delete an existing auto part (Assuming ID 1 is still there)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/parts/1

### Attempt to delete a non-existent auto part
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/parts/999